{"id": "art-250", "label": "Art. 250", "title": "Art. 250", "slug": "art-250", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 250 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_945615392\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1747\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_945615392\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Fuziunea sau\ndivizarea are urm&#259;toarele <span class=SpellE>consecin&#355;e</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_453467839\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1746\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_453467839\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)transferul, atât în raporturile dintre societatea\nabsorbit&#259; sau divizat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> societatea\nabsorbant&#259;/<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare,\ncât <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în raporturile cu <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ii</span>,\nc&#259;tre societatea absorbant&#259; sau fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare al tuturor activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite/divizate; acest transfer va\nfi efectuat în conformitate cu regulile de repartizare stabilite în proiectul\nde fuziune/divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1367149500\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1745\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1367149500\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbite sau divizate devin <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>,\nrespectiv <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbante, respectiv ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare, în conformitate cu regulile de repartizare stabilite în proiectul\nde fuziune/ divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1434775465\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1744\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1434775465\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)societatea absorbit&#259; sau divizat&#259;\nînceteaz&#259; s&#259; existe.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1567547290\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1743\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1567547290\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Nicio <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> sau parte social&#259; la societatea\nabsorbant&#259; nu poate fi schimbat&#259; pentru <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale emise de societatea absorbit&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care sunt <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1956355948\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1742\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1956355948\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)de c&#259;tre societatea absorbant&#259;, direct sau prin\nintermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume\npropriu, dar în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>; sau</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_242382771\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1741\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_242382771\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)de c&#259;tre societatea absorbit&#259;, direct sau prin\nintermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume\npropriu, dar în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_4679251\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1740\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_4679251\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Nicio <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> sau parte social&#259; la una dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare nu poate fi\nschimbat&#259; pentru <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> la societatea\ndivizat&#259;, <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1681426628\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1739\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1681426628\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)de c&#259;tre societatea beneficiar&#259; în cauz&#259;,\ndirect sau prin intermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span>\nîn nume propriu, dar pe seama <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;\nsau</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_422200522\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1738\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_422200522\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)de c&#259;tre societatea divizat&#259;, direct sau prin\nintermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume\npropriu, dar pe seama <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}